	   <tr><td colspan=2>Maybe, maybe not.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you take into account the cost of the vials (even if you make them), the suspensions and the ingredients if you purchase them, it's costing me a fortune for every skill point raise.<br><br>Just using an arbitrary figures of 1 skill increase for every 10 attempts and 5pp for all the ingredients then 50pp for a guaranteed skill increase is well worth it.  Admittedly you don't end up with the poisons, but I would rather be getting xp then farming endless greens for their drops for one skill increase.<br><br>No matter how you raise your skill in poisoning it's going to be very expensive, I don't even want to think how much once I start having to use sealed vials and etheral suspensions, but the point I was trying make was that using your training points is the most painless way. <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
